{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      \"Operator-First\" — We Run AI, Not Just Sell It\n      Hero: \"We Run AI Across 30 Companies. Now We'll Run It For Yours.\"\n      Strategy: Lead with CY's real business portfolio as proof. Show the 30+ companies, RM savings, real revenue numbers. The AI tools are the PRODUCT of running real businesses — not theoretical consulting.\n      Structure: Hero → Stats Bar (30+ companies, 300+ staff, RM saved) → \"The Problem\" (AI consultants who never ran a business) → \"Our Story\" (operator journey) → TrueAI Product → Portfolio Grid (8 SaaS tools) → Pricing (RM12K + RM3K/mo | RM68K All-In) → Case Studies → CTA\n      Visual: Clean white, bold blue (#116DFF), real team/office photos, product screenshots. Mobile-first. No dark mode.\n      Differentiator: Nobody else in Malaysia can say this. Agmo has 250 people but zero operating businesses. Entermind has ex-Accenture cred but no SME operations.\n      RECOMMENDED — This is your undefendable moat","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1774294924408}
